Reasoning: 
1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on congestion control algorithms in computer networks, which falls under the scope of this sub-category. 
2. cs.COMM (Communication and Information Theory) - The paper deals with the performance evaluation and interactions of different congestion control algorithms, which is related to communication and information theory. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the control of network congestion, which is related to systems and control. 
4. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper may touch upon security concerns related to congestion control algorithms in computer networks. 
5. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper may discuss the distributed nature of congestion control algorithms in computer networks.
